pageContext.claim: “Oklahoma is they've done very well, with respect to the rally—with respect to the…they have a really good arena, but they've done very well, with respect to the, I call it the plague. The plague that was sent by China. And I think that, you know, the numbers are very small.”
pageContext.analysis: The weekly average of covid-19 cases in Oklahoma doubled in the week before Trump's Tulsa rally -- and then continued to climb.
